				<span style="color:#1e90ff;">Startling Crawler</span>  
				is a simple web Crawler which identifies for all the forward links in the given web-url. 
				It opens the supplied web-url and the crawls that url. <span style="color:#1e90ff;">Startling Crawler</span> 
				 uses the following python modules 
				for performing its operations:
					<ul style="color:#1e90ff;">
